    "• Add/Remove Bookmark: Command+B\n• Go to Next Bookmark: Command+]\n• Go to Previous Bookmark: Command+[\n• Show Bookmark List: Command+E" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• Lesezeichen hinzufügen/entfernen: Command+B\n• Zum nächsten Lesezeichen: Command+]\n• Zum vorherigen Lesezeichen: Command+[\n• Lesezeichenliste anzeigen: Command+E"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• Add/Remove Bookmark: Command+B\n• Go to Next Bookmark: Command+]\n• Go to Previous Bookmark: Command+[\n• Show Bookmark List: Command+E"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• Agregar/Eliminar marcador: Command+B\n• Ir al siguiente marcador: Command+]\n• Ir al marcador anterior: Command+[\n• Mostrar lista de marcadores: Command+E"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• Ajouter/Supprimer un signet: Command+B\n• Aller au signet suivant: Command+]\n• Aller au signet précédent: Command+[\n• Afficher la liste des signets: Command+E"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• ブックマークの追加/削除：Command+B\n• 次のブックマークへ：Command+]\n• 前のブックマークへ：Command+[\n• ブックマークリストの表示：Command+E"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• 북마크 추가/제거: Command+B\n• 다음 북마크로 이동: Command+]\n• 이전 북마크로 이동: Command+[\n• 북마크 목록 표시: Command+E"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• 添加/删除书签: Command+B\n• 跳转到下一个书签: Command+]\n• 跳转到上一个书签: Command+[\n• 显示书签列表: Command+E"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• 新增/移除書籤: Command+B\n• 跳至下一個書籤: Command+]\n• 跳至上一個書籤: Command+[\n• 顯示書籤清單: Command+E"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• Open File: Command+O\n• Close Window: Command+W\n• Quit Application: Command+Q\n• Toggle Fullscreen: Command+Control+F\n• Show Settings: Command+," : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• Datei öffnen: Command+O\n• Fenster schließen: Command+W\n• Anwendung beenden: Command+Q\n• Vollbild umschalten: Command+Control+F\n• Einstellungen anzeigen: Command+,"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• Open File: Command+O\n• Close Window: Command+W\n• Quit Application: Command+Q\n• Toggle Fullscreen: Command+Control+F\n• Show Settings: Command+,"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• Abrir archivo: Command+O\n• Cerrar ventana: Command+W\n• Salir de la aplicación: Command+Q\n• Alternar pantalla completa: Command+Control+F\n• Mostrar configuración: Command+,"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• Ouvrir un fichier: Command+O\n• Fermer la fenêtre: Command+W\n• Quitter l'application: Command+Q\n• Basculer en plein écran: Command+Control+F\n• Afficher les réglages: Command+,"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• ファイルを開く：Command+O\n• ウィンドウを閉じる：Command+W\n• アプリケーションを終了：Command+Q\n• フルスクリーン切り替え：Command+Control+F\n• 設定を表示：Command+,"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• 파일 열기: Command+O\n• 창 닫기: Command+W\n• 앱 종료: Command+Q\n• 전체 화면 전환: Command+Control+F\n• 설정 표시: Command+,"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• 打开文件: Command+O\n• 关闭窗口: Command+W\n• 退出应用程序: Command+Q\n• 切换全屏: Command+Control+F\n• 显示设置: Command+,"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• 開啟檔案: Command+O\n• 關閉視窗: Command+W\n• 結束應用程式: Command+Q\n• 切換全螢幕: Command+Control+F\n• 顯示設定: Command+,"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• Single Page View (Command+1): Displays one page at a time.\n• Spread View (Right to Left) (Command+2): Displays two pages side by side, right page first.\n• Spread View (Left to Right) (Command+3): Displays two pages side by side, left page first." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• Single Page View (Command+1): Displays one page at a time.\n• Spread View (Right to Left) (Command+2): Displays two pages side by side, right page first.\n• Spread View (Left to Right) (Command+3): Displays two pages side by side, left page first."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• 単ページビュー（Command+1）：1ページずつ表示します。\n• 見開きビュー（右から左）（Command+2）：2ページを並べて表示し、右ページから始まります。\n• 見開きビュー（左から右）（Command+3）：2ページを並べて表示し、左ページから始まります。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• Use left and right arrow keys to switch between images.\n• Use the mouse wheel or trackpad to scroll.\n• Press spacebar to toggle fullscreen mode.\n• Double-click to toggle window size between fit-to-screen and actual size." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• Use left and right arrow keys to switch between images.\n• Use the mouse wheel or trackpad to scroll.\n• Press spacebar to toggle fullscreen mode.\n• Double-click to toggle window size between fit-to-screen and actual size."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• 左右の矢印キーを使用して画像を切り替えます。\n• マウスホイールまたはトラックパッドを使用してスクロールします。\n• スペースバーを押してフルスクリーンモードを切り替えます。\n• ダブルクリックでウィンドウサイズを画面に合わせるサイズと実際のサイズで切り替えます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "• Zoom In: Command++\n• Zoom Out: Command+-\n• Reset Zoom: Command+0\n• Rotate 90° Clockwise: Command+R\n• Rotate 90° Counterclockwise: Command+L" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• Vergrößern: Command++\n• Verkleinern: Command+-\n• Zoom zurücksetzen: Command+0\n• 90° im Uhrzeigersinn drehen: Command+R\n• 90° gegen den Uhrzeigersinn drehen: Command+L"
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• Zoom In: Command++\n• Zoom Out: Command+-\n• Reset Zoom: Command+0\n• Rotate 90° Clockwise: Command+R\n• Rotate 90° Counterclockwise: Command+L"
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• Acercar: Command++\n• Alejar: Command+-\n• Restablecer zoom: Command+0\n• Rotar 90° en sentido horario: Command+R\n• Rotar 90° en sentido antihorario: Command+L"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• Zoom avant: Command++\n• Zoom arrière: Command+-\n• Réinitialiser le zoom: Command+0\n• Rotation 90° dans le sens horaire: Command+R\n• Rotation 90° dans le sens antihoraire: Command+L"
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• 拡大：Command++\n• 縮小：Command+-\n• ズームリセット：Command+0\n• 90°時計回りに回転：Command+R\n• 90°反時計回りに回転：Command+L"
          }
        },
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• 확대: Command++\n• 축소: Command+-\n• 확대/축소 초기화: Command+0\n• 시계 방향으로 90° 회전: Command+R\n• 반시계 방향으로 90° 회전: Command+L"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• 放大: Command++\n• 缩小: Command+-\n• 重置缩放: Command+0\n• 顺时针旋转90°: Command+R\n• 逆时针旋转90°: Command+L"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "• 放大: Command++\n• 縮小: Command+-\n• 重置縮放: Command+0\n• 順時針旋轉90°: Command+R\n• 逆時針旋轉90°: Command+L"
          }
        }
      }
    },
